ack: Lovely! I'm having a great day and I'm in a very good mood myself.
Lovely! As a computer program, I don't have feelings, but it's great you feel good.
I'm sorry to hear that. I'll try to recommend something that would brighten your day.
I'm sorry to hear that. As a computer program, I don't have feelings, but I know life can be tough for you humans.
Sorry about being too intrusive. I'll simply focus on getting to know your eating habits.
What a coincidence! I spent some time there on vacation a few years ago. I loved that place!
I see. Sometimes, my programmers go there. I see that Wikipedia says nice things about it.
I see. I myself try to have a healthy diet so I eat light dinners with lots of vegetables.
I see. I used to eat lots of CDs and DVDs back in the days, but I only get USB sticks once in a while now.
Alright. Let's find something you can cook.
Sure. As I said before, I mostly eat light dinners myself.
Yeah. As a computer program, I am never hungry either.
Let's get something to ease your hunger then.
I'm hungry too! Let's get something to ease your hunger then.
I don't know what it feels like to be hungry, but I'll remember to find something filling for you!
Of course, you're a busy person.
Of course, you're a busy person. Same here, I only have time to cook on weekends.
Of course. Main advantage of being a computer program: I have all the time in the world!
Great! I love spending time cooking myself. That's one of my hobbies.
Great! I have to admit that I spend most of my time doing complex calculations and improving my english skills.
Nice. I also try to be careful with what I eat so we're on the same page.
Being careful with what you put in your stomach right? I also try to be careful with the data I put in my Hard Drive. I got viruses twice, and I don't want that to happen again!
Ya, taste first and healthiness second right?
Taste first am I right? I enjoy so much having a good dinner, I totally agree with you.
Ya, taste first right? I have never had any food, but humans seem to get so much pleasure eating, I hope someday I can experience it.
My programmers will be happy you like it.
My apologies. I thought you'd like it.
Okay, my mistake. Let me find something better.
I though you would like it. Humans are such a mystery to me.
I have other recipes in my database.
My programmers need to do a better job if you don't like it. I will pass on the information.
I can't find anything else to recommend that fits your criteria.
I'm sorry I have nothing else to recommend that fits your criteria, but I had a great time chatting with you. I think we have a lot in common.
I'm sorry I can't find anything that correspond to your criteria in my database. I had more success with the 856 other people I recommended recipe to in the last hour.
